# Product (FridgeWise / TrueSight)

Canonical product docs: **`docs/product/`** (`@docs/product/roadmap.md`, `domain-model.md`, `user-stories.md`, `project-brief.md`).

When roadmap or scope changes, update `docs/product/` first, then `.awp-workspace/1-design/ROADMAP.yaml` and related registers.

## Problem

Users don't remember everything in their fridge. Perishables expire before use — the cost of not knowing is high. Personal waste is the primary MVP focus; charity/food-bank use cases are ideation only (IDEA-007).

## Solution

Log inventory → recipe suggestions from available ingredients → deduct inventory on recipe acceptance.

## Priorities

1. Manual inventory input (V1)
2. Fridge photo recognition (V2)

**Development order:** Inventory → recipe suggestions → image recognition.

## Versions

- V1: Manual inventory + recipe suggestions + deduction on accept
- V2: Fridge photo → detect → user confirms → inventory

## Delivery

Mobile-first responsive web (PWA-capable). Not a native app for MVP. Target: anyone with a fridge.

## Design constraint

Fully usable on mobile and desktop.
